Annabel ainda estaria viva?

509
00:39:53,171 --> 00:39:57,507
<i>Não estávamos aqui cinco
anos atrás e ela morreu.</i>

510
00:39:59,277 --> 00:40:02,761
<i>Se quiser, eu posso
desmontar esse quarto.</i>

511
00:40:03,514 --> 00:40:04,615
Não!

512
00:40:06,884 --> 00:40:09,384
Vamos manter o quarto.

513
00:40:09,385 --> 00:40:12,255
- Por enquanto.
<i>- Claro!</i>

514
00:40:17,895 --> 00:40:19,429
<i>Ricky! Ricky!</i>

515
00:40:19,430 --> 00:40:21,832
<i>- Ricky! Ricky!
- Ricky! Ricky!</i>

516
00:40:25,570 --> 00:40:27,504
<i>Diesel.</i>

517
00:40:27,505 --> 00:40:28,905
Vem!

518
00:40:28,906 --> 00:40:32,442
Vamos!
Sobe!

519
00:40:32,443 --> 00:40:34,444
Venha aqui!

520
